text: The American League East is a group of baseball teams in the American League of Major League Baseball. It is one of the six divisions in the MLB. There are five teams in this division. Four of the five teams are from the eastern United States, and one team is from Canada. ==Teams in the American League East Division== *Baltimore Orioles *Boston Red Sox *New York Yankees *Tampa Bay Rays *Toronto Blue Jays Category:American League
